  "content": "## Core Types\n\n## ChunkingPipeline\n\n```rust\npub struct ChunkingPipeline {\n    registry: FormatRegistry,\n    estimator: Arc<dyn TokenEstimator>,\n    config: ChunkingConfig,\n}\n\nimpl ChunkingPipeline {\n    /// Process a single source file through the full pipeline.\n    pub fn process(\n        &self,\n        source: &str,\n        meta: &SourceMetadata,\n    ) -> Result<Vec<ProcessedChunk>>;\n\n    /// Batch process multiple source files.\n    pub fn process_batch(\n        &self,\n        files: &[(String, SourceMetadata)],\n    ) -> Result<Vec<ProcessedChunk>>;\n}\n```\n",
